Forward Propagation (36–42)
36. What is forward propagation?

Passing data from input layer to output layer.

37. Formula?
Z = WX+B

A = Activation(Z)
38. What is weighted sum?
Σ(wx)
39. Why multiply weights?

To give importance to features.

